{"tid":1017554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自閉兒突展攻擊傾向還尿床　敏銳媽書包放錄音筆揭「老師霸凌」","createTime":"2019-02-11T13:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T14:43:20.000Z","uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f14e39d4813c030f4a59e5a587b3f2c9ba0ba1a","tid":1017554,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3889/3889850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3889%2F3889850.jpg&h=e3246a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 米麗莎用心扶養康登長大。（圖／翻攝自臉書／Milissa Davis）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國一名母親將患有自閉症的兒子送進特教學校就讀後，兒子便出現攻擊傾向，半夜還會尿床。她驚覺有異，有天在兒子上學前，偷偷將錄音筆打開，放進他的書包裡。等到兒子放學回家後，她才發現心愛的兒子每天都遭受老師的霸凌。<br />\n住在路易斯安那州的米麗莎（Milissa Davis）用心扶養兒子康登（Camden）長大，在他12歲那年，將他送進特教學校就讀。沒想到康登突然開始展現出攻擊傾向，半夜還會在睡夢中尿床，令米麗莎相當憂慮，擔心兒子是否在學校受人欺負。<br />\n這名機警的母親為了找出兒子突然改變的原因，便偷偷在兒子的書包裡放入錄音筆。等到康登放學後，米麗莎趕緊將錄下的音檔打開來聽，結果卻讓她飽受衝擊，因為她清楚聽見2名老師不斷以言語霸凌康登。<br />\n根據錄音檔，2名老師對康登說道，「不過就是寫個單字，有這麼難嗎」、「要是去一般學校的話，根本連1分鐘都撐不了吧」、「有種跟你媽說啊」。充滿歧視和惡意的嘲諷讓米麗莎心痛得流下淚來，也將錄音檔交給媒體，並上傳到社群網站，引發民眾群起撻伐。<br />\n事後，校方罷免2名涉案教師，以平息風波，也針對學生家長召開檢討會，加強教育教師。米麗莎則表示，老師的霸凌對康登造成一些後遺症，但在轉學後，狀況已經逐漸好轉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.boredpanda.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/autistic-boy-hidden-backpack-recorder-teachers-bullying-louisiana-milissa-davis-26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.boredpanda.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fautistic-boy-hidden-backpack-recorder-teachers-bullying-louisiana-milissa-davis-26.jpg&h=72751b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/04/14/17/4B28784800000578-5616049-image-a-24_1523724771370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F17%2F4B28784800000578-5616049-image-a-24_1523724771370.jpg&h=ac6719f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190211/1375653.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190211%2F1375653.htm&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu14Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e5370e7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190211/1375653.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c94da031d21a808eae0541a1135ea8bcd96b2667","tid":1017554,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77225e3c382ab74fae9c1141edf6ad7b8ee0efa1","tid":1017554,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57efb1038d7fdb8574c84161d4fd4133544e235e","tid":1017554,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"家長好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}